en.name: HK XM8 5.56x45 assault rifle (FDE)
en.description: The XM8 is a lightweight assault rifle system developed in the 1990's by Heckler & Koch as a replacement for the M4. While it would ultimately not be accepted, the XM8 is a reliable, light, and modular weapon. How it came to Tarkov is unknown, but it is a welcome addition.
